
    NYPD find UK couple who lost ring during romantic proposal

        

    
        
                
                Image copyright
                  NYPD
                
            
            
        Police in New York have found the couple who got engaged in Times Square on Friday but lost the ring down a grate.The NYPD tweeted on Sunday that arrangements were being made to return the ring to the pair, who are from the UK. CCTV images showed the couple unsuccessfully trying to retrieve the piece of jewellery.But police officers later managed to rescue and clean it.The BBC understands the couple are from the UK. Police said they had now returned home.
    
        

    
        
